d="00:23.390">る</span><span begin="00:23.390" end="00:23.713">目</span><span begin="00:23.713" end="00:23.875">が</span><span begin="00:23.875" end="00:24.208">回</span><span begin="00:24.208" end="00:24.359">る</span><span begin="00:24.359" end="00:24.564">パ</span><span begin="00:24.564" end="00:24.716">ラ</span><span begin="00:24.716" end="00:24.877">レ</span><span begin="00:24.877" end="00:25.317">ル</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">头晕目眩并肩忙碌</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Guruguru me ga mawaru parareru</span></p><p begin="00:27.889" end="00:30.720" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:27.889" end="00:28.050">く</span><span begin="00:28.050" end="00:28.209">る</span><span begin="00:28.209" end="00:28.381">く</span><span begin="00:28.381" end="00:28.691">る</span><span begin="00:28.691" end="00:29.216">走</span><span begin="00:29.216" end="00:29.381">り</span><span begin="00:29.381" end="00:29.697">続</span><span begin="00:29.697" end="00:29.871">け</span><span begin="00:29.871" end="00:30.041">て</span><span begin="00:30.041" end="00:30.209">い</span><span begin="00:30.209" end="00:30.720">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">连续不停跑了一路</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kurukuru hashiri tsuzukete iru</span></p><p begin="00:33.205" end="00:37.401" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:33.205" end="00:33.388">ぴょ</span><span begin="00:33.388" end="00:33.558">ん</span><span begin="00:33.558" end="00:33.820">と</span> <span begin="00:34.058" end="00:34.397">飛</span><span begin="00:34.397" end="00:34.556">び</span><span begin="00:34.556" end="00:34.686">出</span><span begin="00:34.686" end="00:34.864">し</span><span begin="00:34.864" end="00:35.029">て</span><span begin="00:35.029" end="00:35.188">み</span><span begin="00:35.188" end="00:35.381">れ</span><span begin="00:35.381" end="00:35.529">ば</span><span begin="00:35.529" end="00:35.830">無</span><span begin="00:35.830" end="00:36.381">重</span><span begin="00:36.381" end="00:37.401">力</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一跃而起 竟没有重力</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Pyonto tobidashite mireba mujuuryoku</span></p><p begin="00:38.522" end="00:42.862" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:38.522" end="00:38.872">全</span><span begin="00:38.872" end="00:39.223">部</span> <span begin="00:39.373" end="00:39.874">君</span><span begin="00:39.874" end="00:40.029">が</span><span begin="00:40.029" end="00:40.193">連</span><span begin="00:40.193" end="00:40.357">れ</span><span begin="00:40.357" end="00:40.506">て</span><span begin="00:40.506" end="00:40.706">き</span><span begin="00:40.706" end="00:40.868">た</span><span begin="00:40.868" end="00:41.347">宇</span><span begin="00:41.347" end="00:42.862">宙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">都是你 带我到太空里</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zenbu kimi ga tsurete kita uchuu</span></p><p begin="00:43.168" end="00:48.679" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:43.168" end="00:43.524">名</span><span begin="00:43.524" end="00:44.193">前</span><span begin="00:44.193" end="00:44.499">の</span><span begin="00:44.499" end="00:44.842">わ</span><span begin="00:44.842" end="00:45.222">か</span><span begin="00:45.222" end="00:45.376">ん</span><span begin="00:45.376" end="00:45.750">な</span><span begin="00:45.750" end="00:45.892">い</span><span begin="00:45.892" end="00:46.189">お</span><span begin="00:46.189" end="00:46.837">星</span><span begin="00:46.837" end="00:47.524">様</span><span begin="00:47.524" end="00:47.697">じゃ</span><span begin="00:47.697" end="00:47.867">な</span><span begin="00:47.867" end="00:48.034">く</span><span begin="00:48.034" end="00:48.679">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无名的星星 可不是你</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namae no wakannai ohoshisama janakute</span></p><p begin="00:49.182" end="00:53.764" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:49.182" end="00:49.423">で</span><span begin="00:49.423" end="00:49.543">っ</span><span begin="00:49.543" end="00:49.734">か</span><span begin="00:49.734" end="00:50.040">い</span><span begin="00:50.040" end="00:50.486">顔</span><span begin="00:50.486" end="00:50.691">し</span><span begin="00:50.691" end="00:50.872">て</span><span begin="00:50.872" end="00:51.201">い</span><span begin="00:51.201" end="00:51.383">て</span><span begin="00:51.383" end="00:51.545">ね</span><span begin="00:51.545" end="00:51.886">お</span><span begin="00:51.886" end="00:52.357">月</span><span begin="00:52.357" end="00:53.764">様</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你是那月亮 神气得意</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dekkai kao shite ite ne otsukisama</span></p><p begin="00:54.217" end="00:56.348" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:54.217" end="00:54.482">は</span><span begin="00:54.482" end="00:54.563">・</span><span begin="00:54.563" end="00:54.812">な</span><span begin="00:54.812" end="00:54.889">・</span><span begin="00:54.889" end="00:55.136">れ</span><span begin="00:55.136" end="00:55.212">・</span><span begin="00:55.212" end="00:55.458">ら</span><span begin="00:55.458" end="00:55.534">・</span><span begin="00:55.534" end="00:55.670">れ</span><span begin="00:55.670" end="00:55.723">・</span><span begin="00:55.723" end="00:55.988">な</span><span begin="00:55.988" end="00:56.066">・</span><span begin="00:56.066" end="00:56.348">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无·法·再·与·你·分·离</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ha・na・re・ra・re・na・i</span></p><p begin="00:56.348" end="00:59.325" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:56.348" end="00:56.513">そ</span><span begin="00:56.513" end="00:56.691">れ</span><span begin="00:56.691" end="00:56.880">が</span> <span begin="00:56.880" end="00:57.502">BANG</span> <span begin="00:57.502" end="00:58.207">YOU</span> <span begin="00:58.207" end="00:58.440">グ</span><span begin="00:58.440" end="00:58.717">ラ</span><span begin="00:58.717" end="00:58.882">ビ</span><span begin="00:58.882" end="00:59.325">ティ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那就是 BANG YOU Gravity</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore ga BANG YOU gurabiti</span></p><p begin="00:59.530" end="01:01.665" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:59.530" end="00:59.807">か</span><span begin="00:59.807" end="00:59.894">・</span><span begin="00:59.894" end="01:00.124">な</span><span begin="01:00.124" end="01:00.220">・</span><span begin="01:00.220" end="01:00.472">え</span><span begin="01:00.472" end="01:00.565">・</span><span begin="01:00.565" end="01:00.810">て</span><span begin="01:00.810" end="01:00.887">・</span><span begin="01:00.887" end="01:00.994">み</span><span begin="01:00.994" end="01:01.069">・</span><span begin="01:01.069" end="01:01.304">た</span><span begin="01:01.304" end="01:01.398">・</span><span begin="01:01.398" end="01:01.665">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">盼·望·梦·想·能·如·意</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ka・na・e・te・mi・ta・i</span></p><p begin="01:01.665" end="01:04.658" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:01.665" end="01:02.057">君</span><span begin="01:02.057" end="01:02.207">と</span><span begin="01:02.207" end="01:02.889">描</span><span begin="01:02.889" end="01:03.199">い</span><span begin="01:03.199" end="01:03.534">た</span><span begin="01:03.534" end="01:03.782">グ</span><span begin="01:03.782" end="01:04.072">ラ</span><span begin="01:04.072" end="01:04.227">フィ</span><span begin="01:04.227" end="01:04.658">ティ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">和你一起的涂鸦信笔</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi to egaita gurafiti</span></p><p begin="01:04.874" end="01:06.979" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:04.874" end="01:05.132">ゆ</span><span begin="01:05.132" end="01:05.221">・</span><span begin="01:05.221" end="01:05.465">め</span><span begin="01:05.465" end="01:05.558">・</span><span begin="01:05.558" end="01:05.795">は</span><span begin="01:05.795" end="01:05.870">・</span><span begin="01:05.870" end="01:06.096">は</span><span begin="01:06.096" end="01:06.201">・</span><span begin="01:06.201" end="01:06.339">て</span><span begin="01:06.339" end="01:06.403">・</span><span begin="01:06.403" end="01:06.600">な</span><span begin="01:06.600" end="01:06.738">・</span><span begin="01:06.738" end="01:06.979">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">梦·无·止·境·不·停·息</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yu・me・wa・ha・te・na・i</span></p><p begin="01:07.038" end="01:09.931" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:07.038" end="01:07.205">コ</span><span begin="01:07.205" end="01:07.411">コ</span><span begin="01:07.411" end="01:07.509">ロ</span><span begin="01:07.509" end="01:07.875">ひ</span><span begin="01:07.875" end="01:08.196">と</span><span begin="01:08.196" end="01:08.523">つ</span><span begin="01:08.523" end="01:08.879">に</span><span begin="01:08.879" end="01:09.085">イン</span><span begin="01:09.085" end="01:09.384">フィ</span><span begin="01:09.384" end="01:09.554">ニ</span><span begin="01:09.554" end="01:09.931">ティ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">同心一意永无穷期</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro hitotsu ni infiniti</span></p><p begin="01:10.189" end="01:12.374" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:10.210" end="01:10.550">ニュ</span><span begin="01:10.550" end="01:10.873">ー</span><span begin="01:10.873" end="01:11.212">ト</span><span begin="01:11.212" end="01:11.495">ン</span><span begin="01:11.495" end="01:11.717">さ</span><span begin="01:11.717" end="01:12.025">ん</span><span begin="01:12.025" end="01:12.374">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">牛顿都要大为惊奇</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nyuuton-san mo</span></p><p begin="01:12.374" end="01:15.241" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:12.374" end="01:12.844">驚</span><span begin="01:12.844" end="01:13.175">き</span><span begin="01:13.175" end="01:13.727">桃</span><span begin="01:13.727" end="01:13.874">の</span><span begin="01:13.874" end="01:14.049">木</span><span begin="01:14.049" end="01:14.344">山</span><span begin="01:14.344" end="01:14.566">椒</span><span begin="01:14.566" end="01:14.841">の</span><span begin="01:14.841" end="01:15.241">木</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">桃树山椒凑在一起</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">odoroki momo no ki sanshou no ki</span></p><p begin="01:26.546" end="01:31.167" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:26.546" end="01:26.876">青</span><span begin="01:26.876" end="01:27.049">い</span><span begin="01:27.049" end="01:27.370">星</span><span begin="01:27.370" end="01:27.532">抜</span><span begin="01:27.532" end="01:27.715">け</span><span begin="01:27.715" end="01:27.879">出</span><span begin="01:27.879" end="01:28.050">し</span><span begin="01:28.050" end="01:28.463">て</span> <span begin="01:29.215" end="01:29.544">遊</span><span begin="01:29.544" end="01:29.728">び</span><span begin="01:29.728" end="01:29.888">に</span><span begin="01:29.888" end="01:30.026">出</span><span begin="01:30.026" end="01:30.193">か</span><span begin="01:30.193" end="01:30.372">け</span><span begin="01:30.372" end="01:30.529">よ</span><span begin="01:30.529" end="01:30.707">う</span><span begin="01:30.707" end="01:31.167">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">冲出蓝色星球 一起出门游戏</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aoi hoshi nukedashite asobi ni dekakeyou yo</span></p><p begin="01:31.867" end="01:34.241" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:31.867" end="01:32.215">太</span><span begin="01:32.215" end="01:32.538">陽</span><span begin="01:32.538" end="01:32.704">で</span><span begin="01:32.704" end="01:32.853">バ</span><span begin="01:32.853" end="01:33.034">ー</span><span begin="01:33.034" end="01:33.189">ベ</span><span begin="01:33.189" end="01:33.385">キュ</span><span begin="01:33.385" end="01:33.983">ー</span><span begin="01:33.983" end="01:34.241">・・・</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">到太阳上烧烤去…</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Taiyou de baabekyuu...</span></p><p begin="01:34.500" end="01:36.894" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:34.500" end="01:34.568">「</span><span begin="01:34.568" end="01:34.974">えっ、</span><span begin="01:34.974" end="01:35.259">あっ、</span><span begin="01:35.259" end="01:35.486">ちょっ、</span><span begin="01:35.486" end="01:35.787">も、</span><span begin="01:35.787" end="01:35.960">燃</span><span begin="01:35.960" end="01:36.089">え</span><span begin="01:36.089" end="01:36.228">て</span><span begin="01:36.228" end="01:36.376">る</span><span begin="01:36.376" end="01:36.894">ー!!!!」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「哎 啊 等会儿 烧起来了!!!!」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">"E, a, cho, mo, moeteruu!!!!"</span></p><p begin="01:37.208" end="01:41.903" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:37.208" end="01:37.340">火</span><span begin="01:37.340" end="01:37.687">星</span><span begin="01:37.687" end="01:38.015">人</span><span begin="01:38.015" end="01:38.399">捕</span><span begin="01:38.399" end="01:38.551">ま</span><span begin="01:38.551" end="01:38.713">え</span><span begin="01:38.713" end="01:39.184">て</span> <span begin="01:39.887" end="01:40.045">ド</span><span begin="01:40.045" end="01:40.212">ロ</span><span begin="01:40.212" end="01:40.373">ケ</span><span begin="01:40.373" end="01:40.550">イ</span><span begin="01:40.550" end="01:40.724">で</span><span begin="01:40.724" end="01:40.848">も</span><span begin="01:40.848" end="01:41.036">し</span><span begin="01:41.036" end="01:41.217">よ</span><span begin="01:41.217" end="01:41.374">う</span><span begin="01:41.374" end="01:41.903">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">把火星人抓走 来玩警察抓小偷</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kasei jin tsukamaete dorokei demo shiyou yo</span></p><p begin="01:42.557" end="01:47.574" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:42.557" end="01:42.696">う</span><span begin="01:42.696" end="01:42.896">ち</span><span begin="01:42.896" end="01:43.060">ら</span><span begin="01:43.060" end="01:43.217">が</span><span begin="01:43.217" end="01:43.399">手</span><span begin="01:43.399" end="01:43.548">を</span><span begin="01:43.548" end="01:4